<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Unavoided" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Unavoided,</orth> 1) not avoided or shunned: <cit><quote>whose u. eye is murderous,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 56</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) inevitable: <cit><quote>and u. is the danger now,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.268" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 1, 268</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a terrible and u. danger,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.5.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 5, 8</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>all u. is the doom of destiny,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.217" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 217</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>